text: Jaysh al Nukhba (Arabic: جَيْشُ النُّخْبَةِ; originally called Jaysh al- Tahrir) is a Syrian Islamist militant group in the Hama Governorate and Aleppo Governorate of Syria with support from the Turkish government. The group was formed as a combination of 5 brigades, and some got BGM-71 TOW anti-tank missiles which are from the United States. == References == Category:Militant groups Category:Islamist militant groups
title: Jaysh al-Nukhba
